Package: NPDS4Clib
Type: Package
Title: Tools for NPDS Calculation and Lung Nodule Progression
        Assessment (Rcpp-based version of the Python Package NPDS4lib)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hang Yu", email = "hangyustat@ruc.edu.cn", role = c("ctb")),
    person("Jingyu Gui", email = "jingyuGui1999@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Yan Lan", email = "lyannnisme@gmail.com", role = c("aut")))
Description: This package allows users to calculate NPDS statistics and assess 
    the progression of lung nodules using baseline and follow-up CT images. 
    The tools are designed for robust and efficient analysis of medical imaging data. 
    It is an Rcpp-based version of the Python package NPDS4lib, which provides similar 
    functionality for Python users. Portions of this package include code adapted 
    from the 'EBImage' package (https://github.com/aoles/EBImage),(see "bwlabel" function in clear_blrder.cpp file) licensed under LGPL.
